STEPS:

                1.If First=NULL then {print “List empty” STOP};

                2.count=0;

                3.ptr=First;  {point ptr to the 1st node}

                4.While ptr<> NULL repeat Steps 5 to 6

                5.count=count+1;

                6.ptr=NEXT(ptr)  [shift ptr to the next node]

                7.print (‘Number of nodes=’, count)

                8.END
